Troops.Name: Ranger
Troops.Flavor: Carefully selected soldiers that have high combat effectiveness and protection and are also a fair price.

Troops.Name: Yeti
Troops.Flavor: Although it is older Walkeranical armor, it has been retrofitted with two 37mm cannons and will certainly bring you bountiful loot.

Troops.Name: Hummingbird
Troops.Flavor: Small airship more mobile than ground forces. Only accuracy needs to be improved.

Troops.Name: Lurker
Troops.Flavor: This universe's outlaws can't muster up an ounce of compassion between them. Don't buy them! --Former employer.

Troops.Name: Spider
Troops.Flavor: Firepower is extremely fierce and it's extremely mobile but very loud. Soundproofing is necessary. Buy with caution.

Troops.Name: Seagull
Troops.Flavor: Converted from a civilian airship and can provide a degree of aerial fire suppression. Requires two pilots.

Troops.Name: Bomber
Troops.Flavor: First attempt to make heavy weapons launcher portable for soldiers to have a strong advantage when engaging with enemy air forces. Only a strong soldier can easily wield this weapon.

Troops.Name: Shredder
Troops.Flavor: This vehicle is very strange and difficult to handle. The wheels can adapt to most battlefield terrain, and it has quite an advantage when it comes to speed.

Troops.Name: Hind
Troops.Flavor: Owning this guided-missile destroyer means owning air supremacy and, more importantly, only needs one pilot.

Troops.Name: Predator
Troops.Flavor: She is a legend on the battlefield. A spaceship killer. There's nothing else to say.

Troops.Name: XTR
Troops.Flavor: All-terrain armored vehicle modified from the empire's own extra flagship military Walkers and is a hot commodity on the black market. Its capabilities are cutting-edge and complex and come with a few manuals to read.

Troops.Name: Gemini
Troops.Flavor: Catamaran hull design has a hull that maintains a great deal of stability during movement. Fire power configuration is specially customized to be relatively higher than other small vessels.

Troops.Name: Master
Troops.Flavor: Their abilities are unknown, and the only thing that can be understood is that when they fire energy weapons, they are infused with some kind of powerful energy. This causes the enemy to fear them as soon as they see them.

Troops.Name: Mantis
Troops.Flavor: Caterpillar tracked vehicles with a two-track design that guarantees all-terrain movement while still maintaining speed. Equipped with an ion cannon that can instantly destroy any target.

Troops.Name: Death
Troops.Flavor: This specially produced weapon does not conform to the galactic convention. The ion cannon it carries was supposed to never leave the lab: it doesn't matter who wields it because it will backfire on friend or foe...

Troops.Name: Arbiter
Troops.Flavor: Veketa people collect the souls of their fallen soldiers and resurrects them into steel bodies. For them, this is the highest honor.

Troops.Name: Rhino
Troops.Flavor: All-weather, all-terrain, the automatic high energy laser cannon! It is designed to: No matter the time or place, rest assured it will simply and easily wipe out the enemy, without reading the manual.

Troops.Name: Ouranos
Troops.Flavor: Ouranos, Crew, Colossus or Warhammer; no matter what name it goes by, it is always the face of destruction.

Troops.Name: Conqueror
Troops.Flavor: The most powerful warriors from the Centaur System whose bodies are far more uncompromising than steel. Their armor is only for show, and they feel a bit chilly when not donning it.

Troops.Name: Bastion
Troops.Flavor: The shape of the Bastion has always been controversial, and people have always said that it looks like a... erm... toilet, but its power is never doubted.

Troops.Name: Chimera
Troops.Flavor: Chimera is the perfect match of many classic types of design and function and is the pinnacle of the times in many aspects.

Troops.Name: Reaper
Troops.Flavor: No one has seen the Reaper's real face, at least, none that are still breathing.

Troops.Name: Sorceror
Troops.Flavor: Concerning whether the Reaper or Sorceror has a stronger argument, it has never stopped. But a lot of people think the Sorcerer is better looking.

Troops.Name: Champion
Troops.Flavor: Champion is the most advanced Walker controlled by this universe's most powerful soldier. But all warriors must die, and Champion has now changed from being controlled by joysticks to an AI.

Troops.Name: Demon
Troops.Flavor: The Guild version of the Champion, just as handsome, and powerful, but a better bang for your buck!

Troops.Name: Dragon
Troops.Flavor: According to Dragon's settings, It should be bigger than today's, and only the head has now been completed. Why haven't they continued building its body? Because it's already too strong!

Troops.Name: Lord
Troops.Flavor: A discovery of unlimited crystals has brought us the unlimited power of the new era. The first armor made from unlimited crystals is known as "Angel of Death" because it doesn't look too stable.The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Airships. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Death-Angel
Troops.Flavor: Meanwhile, using even more of the unlimited crystals can force this energy to become stable. People say that this is discovered by a child who is pleasant to watch star. The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Gaia
Troops.Flavor: Meanwhile, using even more of the unlimited crystals can force this energy to become stable. People say that this is discovered by a child who is pleasant to watch star. The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Genesis
Troops.Flavor: Three unlimited crystals' unique composition can offer seemingly unlimited power rate. Scientists surmise that it has touched the realm of the gods.The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Airships and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Cronus
Troops.Flavor: To conserve unlimited crystals, single-core systems have been exhaustively researched, seemingly matching Gaia's single-core weapon, named Cronus.The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Airships. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Rhea
Troops.Flavor: Gaia's second generation is called Rhea, and there seems to be nothing special.The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Sirius
Troops.Flavor: After the power problem was rectified, the mad rush to have the most massive ship began, the bigger, the better.The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Airships and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Eye-of-Greed
Troops.Flavor: The Apollo of the Abyss is called the treasure of the galaxy, made invincible with weapons designed by the greatest minds. The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Infantry and Walkers. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Plane-Walker
Troops.Flavor: When the Plane Walker embarks, space seems to compress. The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Walkers and Airships. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: The-Maelstrom
Troops.Flavor: Thanks to Unlimited Crystallization, all common detection methods are unable to gather any information on the Maelstrom. The ultimate killing machine, possessing the attributes of both Airships and Infantry. Can activate two kinds of Skills.

Troops.Name: Transcender
Troops.Flavor: Transcender is the one who keeps the cosmos in balance, mastering the knowledge in time and space ordinary folk could never, which many attribute to luck. Hyperspace infantry can tear space and make it an inexorable force.

Troops.Name: Voidskater
Troops.Flavor: Voidskater is a mysterious being of super-dimensional existence. People have created walkers similar to his shape and abilities, making it the most popular character. Hyperspace walker can tear space and make it an inexorable force.

Troops.Name: The-Origin
Troops.Flavor: The emergence of the Transcender allowed scientists to make breakthroughs in the area of space research, which was quickly applied to military strength. The Origin came into existence. Hyperspace airship can tear space and make it an inexorable force.

Troops.Name: Ether-Djinn
Troops.Flavor: Such a giant driven soley by the power of ether deserves the name miracle in any era.
